channel.title: To await: P16 Lite Release 1
channel.description:
Well this is it, the thread for development notes and current updates on P16 Lite development
What is our goal: -Make a fully working P16, working just like TestScape based sources, compatible with any tut -Less lag, that for sure. -Selfmade Stuff -All NPC's and MANY more..
What is done: (will be updated when something new is done) -New server.java -Faster compiling method -Better ban methods.
For more updates, keep on this thread.
System79 and The Real Java
